2016 WW49 Bakerville/SKX-D Gold Release Announcement (BKC #2)

\n \n \n

DEG Platform Integration Team

\n \n
\n

The DEG platform Integration team announces the release of 2016 WW49 Bakerville/SKX-D Gold release package for Intel internal use. The release is based on OS of\n \n Linux/\n \n VMWare/\n \n Windows\n server. The auto-installer packages are available on the Artifactory server (both SH site and OR site). Any questions please contact Bei, Ling.
